      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">People</a> * Timo Haupt</b>\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:302px;\"><a href=\"/File:TimoHaupts2016.JPG\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/7/76/TimoHaupts2016.JPG/300px-TimoHaupts2016.JPG\" width=\"300\" height=\"225\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/7/76/TimoHaupts2016.JPG/450px-TimoHaupts2016.JPG 1.5x, /images/7/76/TimoHaupts2016.JPG 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:TimoHaupts2016.JPG\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Timo Haupt takes a nap <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></div></div></div> \n<p><b>Timo Alexander Haupt</b>, (né Klaustermeyer)<br />\na German computer scientist in <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Media_studies\">media studies</a> and <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/System_administrator\">system administrator</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>. He holds a <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Diplom\">Diplom</a> degree from <a href=\"/Paderborn_University\" title=\"Paderborn University\">Paderborn University</a> in 2006 with the thesis <i>Change of interaction between humans and machines on the example of chess</i> <sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>. \nTimo is chess player, computer chess aficionado, computer chess journalist in particular affiliated with <a href=\"/Computerschach_und_Spiele\" title=\"Computerschach und Spiele\">Computerschach und Spiele</a>, \ncomputer chess tester, <a href=\"/Category:Opening_Book_Author\" title=\"Category:Opening Book Author\">opening book author</a> and operator, most notably for <a href=\"/Spike\" title=\"Spike\">Spike</a> during the <a href=\"/WCCC_2006\" title=\"WCCC 2006\">WCCC 2006</a>, <a href=\"/Cluster_Toga\" title=\"Cluster Toga\">Cluster Toga</a> at the <a href=\"/WCCC_2008\" title=\"WCCC 2008\">WCCC 2008</a>, <a href=\"/Deep_Sjeng\" title=\"Deep Sjeng\">Deep Sjeng</a> at the <a href=\"/DOCCC_2010\" title=\"DOCCC 2010\">DOCCC 2010</a>, <a href=\"/Protector\" title=\"Protector\">Protector</a> at the <a href=\"/WCCC_2015\" title=\"WCCC 2015\">WCCC 2015</a> and <a href=\"/WCSC_2015\" title=\"WCSC 2015\">WCSC 2015</a>, and <a href=\"/GridGinkgo\" title=\"GridGinkgo\">GridGinkgo</a> at  the <a href=\"/WCCC_2016\" title=\"WCCC 2016\">WCCC 2016</a> and <a href=\"/WCCC_2018\" title=\"WCCC 2018\">WCCC 2018</a>, where he also contributed with own ideas concerning the optimistic <a href=\"/Pondering\" title=\"Pondering\">pondering</a> <a href=\"/Parallel_Search\" title=\"Parallel Search\">parallelization</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>.\nAlong with <a href=\"/Ingo_Alth%C3%B6fer\" title=\"Ingo Althöfer\">Ingo Althöfer</a>, he introduced the concept of <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Advanced_Chess\">freestyle chess</a> within a Blitz tournament in August 2004 <sup id=\"cite_ref-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup> <sup id=\"cite_ref-6\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup>.\nIn 2002, Timoe Klaustermeyer was intern for the <a href=\"/ChessBase\" title=\"ChessBase\">ChessBase</a> website team, and later worked for <a href=\"/Dieter_Steinwender\" title=\"Dieter Steinwender\">Steinwender's</a> <i>EDV-Beratung</i> <sup id=\"cite_ref-7\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-7\">&#91;7&#93;</a></sup> <sup id=\"cite_ref-8\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-8\">&#91;8&#93;</a></sup> . \n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Photos\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Photos</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#WCCC_2006\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">WCCC 2006</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#WCCC_2008\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">WCCC 2008</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#WCCC_2015\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">WCCC 2015</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#Selected_Publications\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Selected Publications</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Photos\">Photos</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Timo_Haupt&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Photos\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"WCCC_2006\">WCCC 2006</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Timo_Haupt&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: WCCC 2006\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"floatnone\"><a href=\"/File:TimoAlexWCCC2006.JPG\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"TimoAlexWCCC2006.JPG\" src=\"/images/thumb/e/e1/TimoAlexWCCC2006.JPG/640px-TimoAlexWCCC2006.JPG\" width=\"640\" height=\"474\" style=\"vertical-align: text-bottom\" class=\"thumbborder\" srcset=\"/images/e/e1/TimoAlexWCCC2006.JPG 1.5x\" /></a></div>  \n<p><a href=\"/WCCC_2006\" title=\"WCCC 2006\">WCCC 2006</a> Blitz: <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Timo Klaustermeyer</a> and <a href=\"/Alex_Brunetti\" title=\"Alex Brunetti\">Alex Brunetti</a>, <a href=\"/Delfi\" title=\"Delfi\">Delfi</a> - <a href=\"/Spike\" title=\"Spike\">Spike</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-9\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-9\">&#91;9&#93;</a></sup> <sup id=\"cite_ref-10\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-10\">&#91;10&#93;</a></sup> \n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"WCCC_2008\">WCCC 2008</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Timo_Haupt&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: WCCC 2008\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"floatnone\"><a href=\"http://www.czyzewski.org/sebi/WCCC-Beijing-2008/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img alt=\"Cluster-toga-vs-hiarcs.JPG\" src=\"/images/thumb/2/20/Cluster-toga-vs-hiarcs.JPG/640px-Cluster-toga-vs-hiarcs.JPG\" width=\"640\" height=\"429\" style=\"vertical-align: text-bottom\" class=\"thumbborder\" srcset=\"/images/2/20/Cluster-toga-vs-hiarcs.JPG 1.5x\" /></a></div> \n<p><a href=\"/WCCC_2008\" title=\"WCCC 2008\">WCCC 2008</a>, round 1, <a href=\"/Harvey_Williamson\" title=\"Harvey Williamson\">Harvey Williamson</a> and <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Timo Klaustermeyer</a>, <a href=\"/Cluster_Toga\" title=\"Cluster Toga\">Cluster Toga</a> - <a href=\"/HIARCS\" title=\"HIARCS\">HIARCS</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-11\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-11\">&#91;11&#93;</a></sup> <sup id=\"cite_ref-12\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-12\">&#91;12&#93;</a></sup> \n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"WCCC_2015\">WCCC 2015</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Timo_Haupt&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: WCCC 2015\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"floatnone\"><a href=\"/File:ProtectorShredderWCCC2015.JPG\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"ProtectorShredderWCCC2015.JPG\" src=\"/images/5/5a/ProtectorShredderWCCC2015.JPG\" width=\"640\" height=\"480\" style=\"vertical-align: text-bottom\" class=\"thumbborder\" /></a></div> \n<p><a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Timo Haupt</a> and <a href=\"/Stefan_Meyer-Kahlen\" title=\"Stefan Meyer-Kahlen\">Stefan Meyer-Kahlen</a> at the <a href=\"/WCCC_2015\" title=\"WCCC 2015\">WCCC 2015</a> in <a href=\"/Protector\" title=\"Protector\">Protector</a> - <a href=\"/Shredder\" title=\"Shredder\">Shredder</a>  <sup id=\"cite_ref-13\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-13\">&#91;13&#93;</a></sup> \n</p>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Selected_Publications\">Selected Publications</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Timo_Haupt&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: Selected Publications\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Timo Klaustermeyer</a> (<b>2006</b>). <i>Wandel von Interaktion zwischen Menschen und Maschine am Beispiel des Schachspiels</i>. Diplom thesis, <a href=\"/Paderborn_University\" title=\"Paderborn University\">Paderborn University</a>, advisors <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://dblp.uni-trier.de/pers/hd/s/Szwillus:Gerd\">Gerd Szwillus</a> and <a href=\"/Ingo_Alth%C3%B6fer\" title=\"Ingo Althöfer\">Ingo Althöfer</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.team-oh.de/files/Abstract%20Diplomarbeit.pdf\">abstract as pdf</a> (German)</li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Timo_Haupt&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.team-oh.de/\">Timo Haupt</a></li></ul>\n<dl><dd> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.team-oh.de/Computerschach/Clash.htm\">Clash of the Titans</a></dd></dl>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.game-ai-forum.org/icga-tournaments/person.php?id=593\">Timo Klaustermeyer's ICGA Tournaments</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Timo_Haupt&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap mw-references-columns\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">Operating <a href=\"/GridGinkgo\" title=\"GridGinkgo\">GridGinkgo</a> is exhausting and at times tiring - Timo Haupt takes a nap during the <a href=\"/WCCC_2016\" title=\"WCCC 2016\">WCCC 2016</a>, Photo by <a href=\"/Gerd_Isenberg\" title=\"Gerd Isenberg\">Gerd Isenberg</a>, ‎June 28, ‎2016</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.xing.com/profile/Timo_Haupt3\">Timo Haupt - IT Administrator | XING</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Timo Klaustermeyer</a> (<b>2006</b>). <i>Wandel von Interaktion zwischen Menschen und Maschine am Beispiel des Schachspiels</i>. Diplom thesis, <a href=\"/Paderborn_University\" title=\"Paderborn University\">Paderborn University</a>, advisors <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://dblp.uni-trier.de/pers/hd/s/Szwillus:Gerd\">Gerd Szwillus</a> and <a href=\"/Ingo_Alth%C3%B6fer\" title=\"Ingo Althöfer\">Ingo Althöfer</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.team-oh.de/files/Abstract%20Diplomarbeit.pdf\">abstract as pdf</a> (German)</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-4\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://icga.org/?page_id=2429\">2018 Chess Program Descriptions | ICGA</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-5\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a href=\"/Ingo_Alth%C3%B6fer\" title=\"Ingo Althöfer\">Ingo Althöfer</a> (<b>2018</b>). <i>Computer-Aided Game Play and Computer Cheating: Examples from Chess, Shogi, and Go</i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.uni-trier.de/fileadmin/fb4/prof/BWL/FIN/Veranstaltungen/pisa-althofer-12.pdf\">Extended Abstract as pdf</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-6\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-6\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.team-oh.de/FreestyleBlitz/Rules.htm\">Freestyle Blitz Tournaments on January 15 and 22, 2005</a> by <a href=\"/Ingo_Alth%C3%B6fer\" title=\"Ingo Althöfer\">Ingo Althöfer</a> and <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Timo Klaustermeyer</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-7\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-7\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.steinwender.de/cms/front_content.php\">Steinwender EDV-Beratung</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-8\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-8\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.team-oh.de/Lebenslauf.htm\">Timo Haupt - CV</a> (German)</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-9\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-9\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">Photo by <a href=\"/Gerd_Isenberg\" title=\"Gerd Isenberg\">Gerd Isenberg</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-10\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-10\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.game-ai-forum.org/icga-tournaments/tournament.php?id=17\">14th World Computer Chess Championship (Blitz) - Turin 2006</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-11\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-11\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.czyzewski.org/sebi/WCCC-Beijing-2008/\">Index of /sebi/WCCC-Beijing-2008</a> pictures by <a href=\"/Sebastian_B%C3%B6hme\" title=\"Sebastian Böhme\">Sebastian Böhme</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-12\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-12\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.game-ai-forum.org/icga-tournaments/round.php?tournament=178&amp;round=1&amp;id=3\">Beijing 2008 - Chess - Round 1 - Game 3 (ICGA Tournaments)</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-13\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-13\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">Photo by <a href=\"/Gerd_Isenberg\" title=\"Gerd Isenberg\">Gerd Isenberg</a></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n<p><b><a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">Up one level</a></b>\n</p>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260301005923\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.029 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.034 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 213/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node coun